729965f-a.title: Richmond: York Avenue - Buchanan Street
729965f-a.text:
137 to 163 York Avenue, east side, between Buchanan
and Carlyle Streets, looking south toward the latter. The
first two houses (Nos. 137 and 141) belonged in 1874 to
Crabtree; the third house (No. 145) was owned by Birtwistle,
and the fourth one (No. 149-151) by R. Hartley. (See Beers's map.)
July 21, 1932
